  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/8e142dd6152d3df2f1a15733352970a9.avif?t=1749049260\" width=616 height=280 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The long-awaited game adaptation of Natsume’s Book of Friends is here!</strong></h2>Step into the shoes of Takashi Natsume and spend an unforgettable summer vacation.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Spend an unforgettable summer as Takashi Natsume</strong></h2>The first term is over and summer vacation has finally begun.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/cc7b28f33a3be742c68d3a6afc4fd366.poster.avif?t=1749049260\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/cc7b28f33a3be742c68d3a6afc4fd366.webm?t=1749049260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/cc7b28f33a3be742c68d3a6afc4fd366.mp4?t=1749049260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Natsume weaves heartwarming stories through his encounters with various people.<br>Unravel their stories when you complete their requests.<br>There are five possible endings.<br>Enjoy an original story unique to the game—an experience you won’t find anywhere else.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Strengthen Bonds Through “Gifts”</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/2616271b08701ab780d807cf0fc6cb2b.avif?t=1749049260\" width=616 height=320 /></span><br>Collect a variety of items by fulfilling requests or shopping in town.<br>Gift these to your friends and strengthen your bonds.<br>You might surprise them, make them smile, or receive an unexpected response—<br>New requests appear as your bonds strengthen!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Packed with Classic Summer Events</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/9499bc925df7bbfc2f2504a791c498ac.poster.avif?t=1749049260\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/9499bc925df7bbfc2f2504a791c498ac.webm?t=1749049260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Festivals, test of courage, fireworks displays...<br>Enjoy a lineup of nostalgic summer events.<br>Each moment is sure to become a lasting memory.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Beautifully Recreated World of Natsume’s Book of Friends</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/e485e30a7b12e4840ed13e91a9a789be.poster.avif?t=1749049260\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/e485e30a7b12e4840ed13e91a9a789be.webm?t=1749049260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Warm and gently nostalgic.<br>Immerse yourself in the vibrant world and live out your days as “Natsume.”<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Journey Through Fond Memories</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/5707520e63dccb1d6de6fc50729224c8.poster.avif?t=1749049260\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/5707520e63dccb1d6de6fc50729224c8.webm?t=1749049260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Those precious encounters, those heartfelt emotions...<br>Some requests will bring back memorable scenes from Seasons 1 through 7 of the anime.<br>Relive Natsume’s journey and reflect on the path he has walked.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/8e142dd6152d3df2f1a15733352970a9.avif?t=1749049260\" width=616 height=280 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The long-awaited game adaptation of Natsume’s Book of Friends is here!</strong></h2>Step into the shoes of Takashi Natsume and spend an unforgettable summer vacation.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Spend an unforgettable summer as Takashi Natsume</strong></h2>The first term is over and summer vacation has finally begun.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/cc7b28f33a3be742c68d3a6afc4fd366.poster.avif?t=1749049260\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/cc7b28f33a3be742c68d3a6afc4fd366.webm?t=1749049260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/cc7b28f33a3be742c68d3a6afc4fd366.mp4?t=1749049260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Natsume weaves heartwarming stories through his encounters with various people.<br>Unravel their stories when you complete their requests.<br>There are five possible endings.<br>Enjoy an original story unique to the game—an experience you won’t find anywhere else.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Strengthen Bonds Through “Gifts”</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/2616271b08701ab780d807cf0fc6cb2b.avif?t=1749049260\" width=616 height=320 /></span><br>Collect a variety of items by fulfilling requests or shopping in town.<br>Gift these to your friends and strengthen your bonds.<br>You might surprise them, make them smile, or receive an unexpected response—<br>New requests appear as your bonds strengthen!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Packed with Classic Summer Events</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/9499bc925df7bbfc2f2504a791c498ac.poster.avif?t=1749049260\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/9499bc925df7bbfc2f2504a791c498ac.webm?t=1749049260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Festivals, test of courage, fireworks displays...<br>Enjoy a lineup of nostalgic summer events.<br>Each moment is sure to become a lasting memory.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Beautifully Recreated World of Natsume’s Book of Friends</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/e485e30a7b12e4840ed13e91a9a789be.poster.avif?t=1749049260\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/e485e30a7b12e4840ed13e91a9a789be.webm?t=1749049260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Warm and gently nostalgic.<br>Immerse yourself in the vibrant world and live out your days as “Natsume.”<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Journey Through Fond Memories</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/5707520e63dccb1d6de6fc50729224c8.poster.avif?t=1749049260\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344960/extras/5707520e63dccb1d6de6fc50729224c8.webm?t=1749049260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Those precious encounters, those heartfelt emotions...<br>Some requests will bring back memorable scenes from Seasons 1 through 7 of the anime.<br>Relive Natsume’s journey and reflect on the path he has walked.",
